dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.systemtemplate.fibex.fibex4ethernet.ethernetcommunication

Interface ISocketAddress

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface ISocketAddress
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    ISocketAddress: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class represents a socket address towards the rest of the meta-model. The actual semantics of the represented socket address, however, is contributed by aggregation of an ApplicationEndpoint.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
